{"type":"message","id":"def7d247","parentId":"9a93f7fb","timestamp":"2026-04-09T19:02:11.678Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_RX9cn9Zv9AATQM0TY1lx36Ri","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"﻿---\ndate: 2026-03-26\ntime: 00:24\nsession_id: 20260326002400\nagent: andrew-main\ntype: session\nsource: memory/2026-03-26.md\ntags: [framework, implementation, ecc-integration]\nrelated_sessions: []\ndecisions: [ADR-001, ADR-002, ADR-003, ADR-004, ADR-005]\nprojects: [PROJ-001]\n---\n\n# Session 2026-03-26: Framework Completion\n\n## Zusammenfassung\nKomplette Implementierung des Modular Agent Frameworks mit ECC-Integration.\n90+ Dateien erstellt, 27/27 Validierungen bestanden.\n\n## Getroffene Entscheidungen\n- [x] [[ADR-001|YAML vs JSON]] - Architektur-Entscheidung\n- [x] [[ADR-002|File-based vs Database]] - Speicher-Strategie\n- [x] [[ADR-003|SKILL.md Format]] - Skill-Standard\n- [x] [[ADR-004|Hybrid Error Handling]] - Fehlerbehandlung\n- [x] [[ADR-005|MCP Integration Prep]] - Erweiterbarkeit\n\n## Erstellte Komponenten\n- ✅ 4 Phasen (Registry, Cognitive, Persistence, Operations)\n- ✅ 6 Spezialisierte Agenten\n- ✅ 11 Skills\n- ✅ 22 Commands\n- ✅ 3 Contexts (dev, research, review)\n- ✅ GitHub Actions (3 Workflows)\n- ✅ MCP Configs (6 Server)\n- ✅ Second Brain (PARA-System)\n\n## Statistiken\n- **Dateien:** 90+\n- **Validierung:** 27/27 (100%)\n- **Version:** 1.3.0\n- **Status:** Production Ready\n\n## Verknüpfungen\n- Framework: [[../../README|Modular Agent Framework]]\n- Session Summary: [[C:/Users/andre/Documents/Andrew Openclaw/session-summary|Externe Zusammenfassung]]\n- Dashboard: [[00-Dashboard/Dashboard|Dashboard]]\n\n## Code-Blöcke extrahiert\n- [[03-Resources/CodeBlocks/|Siehe CodeBlocks]]\n\n## Tags\n#framework #implementation #ecc-integration #complete\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775761331670}}
