{"type":"message","id":"f0958f8f","parentId":"9be8e074","timestamp":"2026-04-09T19:07:40.068Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_2Obkz5ww9DtqnphkqoS27KhI","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\ndate: {{date:YYYY-MM-DD}}\nadr_id: ADR-XXX\ntitle: \nstatus: Proposed\npriority: Medium\ntags: [adr, architecture]\n---\n\n# ADR-XXX: {{title}}\n\n## Status\n\n- [ ] Proposed\n- [ ] Under Review\n- [ ] Accepted\n- [ ] Deprecated\n- [ ] Superseded by: ADR-YYY\n\n---\n\n## Kontext\n\n> Was ist der Hintergrund? Welches Problem lösen wir?\n\n---\n\n## Entscheidung\n\n> Was wurde entschieden?\n\n---\n\n## Konsequenzen\n\n### Positiv\n\n- \n- \n\n### Negativ\n\n- \n- \n\n---\n\n## Alternativen\n\n| Alternative | Pros | Cons |\n|-------------|------|------|\n| Option A |  |  |\n| Option B |  |  |\n\n---\n\n## Verwandte Entscheidungen\n\n- [[ADR-XXX|Verwandte Entscheidung]]\n\n---\n\n#adr #architecture #decision\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775761660059}}
{"type":"message","id":"cbcd89aa","parentId":"f0958f8f","timestamp":"2026-04-09T19:07:40.078Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_TjvH7lHZCkQtoEJR72E1yYXE","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\ndate: {{date:YYYY-MM-DD}}\ntime: {{time:HH:mm}}\nsession_id: {{date:YYYYMMDDHHmmss}}\nagent: andrew-main\ntokens_in: \ntokens_out: \ncost: \nstatus: active\ntags: []\n---\n\n# Session {{date:YYYY-MM-DD}} {{time:HH:mm}}\n\n## Übersicht\n\n| Attribut | Wert |\n|----------|------|\n| **Datum** | {{date:YYYY-MM-DD}} |\n| **Zeit** | {{time:HH:mm}} |\n| **Agent** | andrew-main |\n| **Status** | active |\n| **Tokens (In)** |  |\n| **Tokens (Out)** |  |\n| **Kosten** |  |\n\n---\n\n## Zusammenfassung\n\n> Kurze Zusammenfassung der Session\n\n---\n\n## Wichtige Erkenntnisse\n\n- \n- \n- \n\n---\n\n## Entscheidungen\n\n- [ ] [[ADR-XXX|Entscheidung 1]]\n- [ ] [[ADR-XXX|Entscheidung 2]]\n\n---\n\n## Code-Snippets\n\n```python\n# Beispiel\n```\n\n---\n\n## Links\n\n- **Vorherige Session**: [[Session-XXXX|← Vorherige]]\n- **Nächste Session**: [[Session-XXXX|Nächste →]]\n- **Projekt**: [[Project-XXXX|Projekt]]\n\n---\n\n#session #{{date:YYYY-MM}}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775761660069}}
{"type":"message","id":"f08666e6","parentId":"cbcd89aa","timestamp":"2026-04-09T19:07:40.084Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_SA3nKYsJfcNlGIVnEDMjUfhi","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\ndate: {{date:YYYY-MM-DD}}\nproject_id: PROJ-XXX\ntitle: \nstatus: Active\nprogress: 0\npriority: Medium\ntags: [project]\n---\n\n# PROJ-XXX: {{title}}\n\n## Übersicht\n\n| Attribut | Wert |\n|----------|------|\n| **Startdatum** | {{date:YYYY-MM-DD}} |\n| **Status** | Active |\n| **Fortschritt** | 0% |\n| **Priorität** | Medium |\n\n---\n\n## Ziel\n\n> Was soll erreicht werden?\n\n---\n\n## Aufgaben\n\n- [ ] Aufgabe 1\n- [ ] Aufgabe 2\n- [ ] Aufgabe 3\n\n---\n\n## Sessions\n\n```dataview\nTABLE date as \"Datum\", summary as \"Zusammenfassung\"\nFROM \"SecondBrain/01-Sessions\"\nWHERE contains(projects, this.project_id)\nSORT date DESC\n```\n\n---\n\n## Entscheidungen\n\n```dataview\nTABLE status as \"Status\", priority as \"Priorität\"\nFROM \"SecondBrain/02-Areas/Decisions\"\nWHERE contains(projects, this.project_id)\nSORT priority DESC\n```\n\n---\n\n## Code-Snippets\n\n```dataview\nLIST\nFROM \"SecondBrain/03-Resources/CodeBlocks\"\nWHERE contains(projects, this.project_id)\n```\n\n---\n\n## Notizen\n\n---\n\n#project #active\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775761660079}}
